 function. Or it could be a list of distance matrices.
}
  \item{data}{
%%     ~~Describe \code{dat} here~~
a data frame containing the covariates
}
  \item{\dots}{
%%     ~~Describe \code{\dots} here~~
parameter passing to \code{adonis} function
}
}

